data.description: $10,000 toward buyer's closing cost! Fantastic split bedroom floorplan! This lovely home features a living room off the entry with a fireplace w/gas logs, tall ceilings, and plenty of natural light. Primary bedroom/bathroom has his/hers closets, double vanity, and separate tub/shower. Kitchen, breakfast area, and dining room offer plenty of space for entertaining. Two more bedrooms and a full bath downstairs with a finished bonus room upstairs. Outside you will find a large patio, wood fence, and above ground pool with wood deck. Exterior recently painted. Call today to schedule your appointment. Buyer to verify schools.
